Introduction

Baek Juho, also known as Zuho is a South Korean rapper, actor, and dancer under Haewadal Entertainment. He is also a member of the boy group SF9.

He debuted as a member of SF9 on October 5, 2016, with the group's first single album "Feeling Sensation".

On January 11th, it was announced that Zuho signed an exclusive contract with the agency Haewadal Entertainment for his solo activities as an actor however, Zuho will continue to serve as an active member of SF9.
